{
  "stem": "16163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was here already in 1947.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I met somebody who knew him and knew him and me, and he told me that he's living in Prague.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got in touch with each other, and we were writing for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But by then, I was married already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we wrote for a while together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had married and had a little boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And tried to get out of Czechoslovakia that time, which was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then later on I found out-- matter of fact, through that friend who was in the resistance, who is here in New York-- that he came to the United States and lived here in New York, in Brooklyn somewhere.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he died about two, three years ago-- four years ago, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We never got in contact with each other, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One of those things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where there are Jewish prayers in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Were-- were holidays celebrated?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were the rabbis from-- who were in Theresienstadt from different towns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if it was allowed or not, but it was done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always [? feel ?] whatever we did included the lessons they gave us, you know, like schooling and things like that-- I always had the feeling that the SS knew, but they also knew we wouldn't make it there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That we would be sent out anyway, the younger [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now with the rabbis, I know that they had services, you know, in different places, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] that's in question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw a nun in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know who she was and how she got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what nationality she was, but I saw her.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
